{"id": 3045, "genre": 1000, "title": "当代生活的哪些细节会让你有一种「异化」的感受？", "description": "工具不再是工具，而变成了目的本身。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 9741, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191031231045rqeWZL36tNBnmOox.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-31T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5999, "title": "当代生活的哪些细节会让你有一种「异化」的感受？", "content": "当代生活的哪些细节会让你有一种「异化」的感受？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349059, "content": "拍照的目的不是记录生活，而是“传到朋友圈好不好看”", "image": "img/option/option/20191031213843urwDHG8BcUaOljCQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349060, "content": "知识本来是让人了解世界，现在只是为了“获取知识感”", "image": "img/option/option/20191031234010KoqQ7VawOHU3nrk2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349061, "content": "玩手机本意是对抗无聊，现在变成“明明很无聊还是要刷”", "image": "img/option/option/20191031214824KTGa5V1vOsHNDwJ4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349062, "content": "网上说话的本意是沟通，现在变成了“发言前要先防杠”", "image": "img/option/option/20191031220342ILmyvNbFwojBZUuT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349063, "content": "走进一家书店，最先被吸引/最想买的往往反而不是书", "image": "img/option/option/20191031221004fTXz2uRVx3ZqYKWm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349064, "content": "关注转发原意是表达认可，现在变成了“比谁更有流量”", "image": "img/option/option/20191031222716mwEAf5KYB26dQ34S.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349065, "content": "多任务的目的从“省时”变成了展示“看我会 multitasking”", "image": "img/option/option/20191031224703QuPzLsM0qVxCOyEY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349066, "content": "工作原本是为了生活，现在反而把人们变成了“社畜”", "image": "img/option/option/20191031225053YrZxmsTbhDiG687S.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349067, "content": "休闲时间从放松变成了“不利用起来就无法自我提升”的焦虑", "image": "img/option/option/20191031234623woe8BjfVD6XnAizE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}